descriptionHtml:
Hi this is my first mod and i hope you like it.
If you have any feedback please let me know.
I appreciate every comment 
I know its not the best mod or player home but i tried my best at making it look good.
The player home is located across riverwood, under the bandit tower 
It has :
-Bedroom
-Crafting area
-Main room with chests


The photos are not the best but bear with me.
author: Tandium
